{
  "title": "Golden Brown Malaysian Pork Tenderloin Skewers",
  "description": "A yeasty and dense Malaysian dish featuring pork tenderloin, perfect for a weeknight dinner, with a low sodium content and caramelized flavor.",
  "cuisine": "Malaysian",
